* write a c program to print any number until the user the print the 0 the program should be ended 


#include <stdio.h>

int main(){
    int i=1;
    int n;
    do{
        printf("Enter your number: ");
        scanf("%d",&n);
        printf("The entered Number is:%d \n",n);
        i++;
    }
    while(n!=0);
    printf("The program is Ended");

    return 0;
}

output
Enter your number: 1
The entered Number is:1 
Enter your number: 0
The entered Number is:0 
The program is Ended
